                  img.social-index-user-img(src="./img/notify_report_full_white.svg")
                  .social-notify-content
                    .social-notify-text-block
                      .social-notify-text 您的<span class="social-notify-report-item">留言內容</span>遭檢舉，經審查後判定 <span class="social-notify-report-punish">給予警告</span>、<span class="social-notify-report-punish">刪除留言</span>
                      .social-notify-time 02.25
                    .btn.social-post-unfollow.btn-social-release.position-relative.social-notify-button(type='button' data-bs-toggle='modal' data-bs-target='#social-notify-report-comment') 詳情瞭解

                //你的帳號被檢舉，審核後停權999天
