                  img.social-index-user-img(src="./img/notify_report_full_white.svg")
                  .social-notify-content
                    .social-notify-text-block
                      .social-notify-text 您的<span class="social-notify-report-item">帳號</span>遭檢舉，經審查後判定 <span class="social-notify-report-punish">停權999天</span>
                      .social-notify-time 01.10
                    .btn.social-post-unfollow.btn-social-release.position-relative.social-notify-button(type='button' data-bs-toggle='modal' data-bs-target='#social-notify-report-account') 詳情瞭解

                //你的帳號因不當檢舉，審核後停權3天
                .social-notify-list
                  img.social-index-user-img(src="./img/notify_report_full_white.svg")
                  .social-notify-content
                    .social-notify-text-block
                      .social-notify-text 您的<span class="social-notify-report-item">帳號</span>因不當檢舉，經審查後判定 <span class="social-notify-report-punish">停權3天</span>
                      .social-notify-time 01.10
                    .btn.social-post-unfollow.btn-social-release.position-relative.social-notify-button(type='button' data-bs-toggle='modal' data-bs-target='#social-notify-report-falsely') 詳情瞭解


    //20220405新增 - 被檢舉文章通知審核結果彈跳視窗
